    public class RequestInfoAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.android.gms.maps.GoogleMap.InfoWindowAdapter
    The purpose of this adapter class is to fit a layout for the information window that appears when the user interacts with a select Donor or Recipient marker on Google Maps
